          <li><strong>Scope</strong> — produce 30 articles per tool over 90 days.</li>
          <li><strong>Measurement</strong> — time per article, on-page SEO score, articles indexed, total cost.</li>
          <li><strong>Total spend</strong> — $2,140 across 10 tools, Mar–May 2026.</li>
