            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Sites that rank on page one publish 20–30 articles per month on average. Consistency beats volume — 8 articles a month every month outperforms 30 one month and 2 the next. Pick a tool whose entry plan matches your sustainable cadence, not your aspirational one.</p></div></div>
